OL,3,CHarry Styles fans camp out for 'One
OL,4,CNight Only' gig
OL,6,F"I love him": Fans from around the
OL,7,Fworld hope camping out overnight will
OL,8,Fsecure them a prime position to watch
OL,9,Ftheir favourite artist's first gig in
OL,10,Fthree years.
OL,12,FDozens of Harry Styles fans have
OL,13,Fcamped out overnight to secure the
OL,14,Fbest spots for his highly anticipated
OL,15,F"One Night Only" performance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
