PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772910673
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans camp out for 'One
OL,4,CNight Only' gig
OL,6,FThe sold-out show in Manchester, which
OL,7,Fcoincides with the release of his
OL,8,Ffourth studio album "Kiss All The
OL,9,FTime. Disco, Occasionally", marks a
OL,10,Fmajor homecoming for the Cheshire-born
OL,11,Fstar.
OL,13,FFans from around the world began
OL,14,Fpitching tents and queuing with
OL,15,Fsleeping bags outside the Co-Op Live
OL,16,Farena as early as Thursday, 5 March,
OL,17,Fdespite the chilly and rainy weather
OL,18,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772910673
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans camp out for 'One
OL,4,CNight Only' gig
OL,6,FOne fan who has been camping out with
OL,7,Ftwo other friends said: "The reason
OL,8,Fwe're here is because the earlier you
OL,9,Fget here, the better spot you get.
OL,11,F"He is my favourite artist since I was
OL,12,F14. I love his music and can't wait to
OL,13,Fhear his new album."
OL,15,FSpeaking outside the arena, one fan
OL,16,Fwho travelled from Florida: "I took
OL,17,Fthree flights to get here - it took 30
OL,18,Fhours - but it is the best. His music
OL,19,Fsaved my life and the community he
OL,20,Fcreated is the best.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772910673
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans camp out for 'One
OL,4,CNight Only' gig
OL,6,FAnother fan who is camping out despite
OL,7,Fnot having a ticket, said: "Maybe a
OL,8,Fmiracle will happen tomorrow. We have
OL,9,Fbeen waiting for three years and I'm
OL,10,Fso excited he is back. I have been a
OL,11,Ffan since I was 12."
OL,13,FTickets cost just #20 and the gig will
OL,14,Fbe a strictly phone-free event, with
OL,15,Ffans required to lock away their
OL,16,Fmobile devices in specialised
OL,17,Frecyclable pouches that stop the use
OL,18,Fof the camera function.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772910673
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans camp out for 'One
OL,4,CNight Only' gig
OL,6,FInstead, ticket holders will be issued
OL,7,Fwith a disposable camera so they can
OL,8,Fstill capture the evening.
OL,10,FThe performance is being documented
OL,11,Ffor a Netflix special, Harry Styles:
OL,12,FOne Night in Manchester, which is set
OL,13,Fto premiere globally this Sunday, 8
OL,14,FMarch.
OL,16,FWhile the exact setlist has not been
OL,17,Freleased, the former One Direction
OL,18,Fsinger will perform his new album for
OL,19,Fthe very first time. The 12-track
OL,20,Falbum was released in the early hours
OL,21,Fof Friday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
