PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772910673
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans camp out for 'One
OL,4,CNight Only' gig
OL,6,FTransport for Greater Manchester
OL,7,F(TfGM) has urged those attending to
OL,8,Fuse the Metrolink or city centre
OL,9,Fshuttle bus service, with free travel
OL,10,Fincluded for all ticket holders on the
OL,11,Fday of the concert.
OL,13,FThe City Venue Link walking route from
OL,14,FManchester Piccadilly railway station
OL,15,Fremains the recommended path for those
OL,16,Farriving by train.
OL,18,FDoors will open at 6pm for premium
OL,19,Fticket holders and 6:30pm for general
OL,20,Fadmission tickets.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
